{
  "stem": "3855.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the local church hierarchy had tremendous influence on the people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And these groups clashed repeatedly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had actual mini civil wars in Vienna, where they were shooting cannons at these fortresses that the working class had built under the guidance of the leadership of the Social Democrats.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was a particular problem, because the leaders of the Social Democrats in Vienna were Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And when Hitler invaded Austria, they fled.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And it led to a tremendous backlash among Gentile workers, who said, you escaped.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "You're out there, and we are here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And they all turned National, Socialistic.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When I was working-- it was obligatory for engineering students to work every summer for a month or two in a factory somewheres to gain practical experience.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And I worked for the largest Austrian diesel engine manufacturers, truck diesels.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I had contact with workers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And they were-- were all very leftist, very.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "But it changed rapidly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Now I want to continue with what you asked me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Naturally, we read, and there was already radio.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We heard Hitler's speeches.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "But being middle class Austrians, and my relatives in Czechoslovakia, never thought that such a thing could happen to us.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It's an interesting phenomenon.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You feel comfortable in your surroundings.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "You're physically comfortable.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And you can't foreseen-- can't foresee this overnight, dramatic change that can take place in people and in your living situation.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And so there was no thought of building ahead and emigrating, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I'll give you an example.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "One of my relatives in Czechoslovakia was extremely well off.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They were in Gablonz, which is the center of artificial jewelry.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he had a factory, and he had 31 representatives throughout the world selling his goods.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "When he escaped to England penniless, he had 31 representatives and nothing.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
